 shark attacks seem ferocious and brutal, sharks are not interested in eating humans. In fact, humans do not provide enough high-fat meat for sharks. Sharks need a lot of energy to power their large and muscular bodies. Sharks attack humans because they mistake humans for what it usually eats.</p><p>Once we start to look at the problem from the perspective of a shark, the confusion of the shark is easier to understand. Many attack victims are surfers or surfboarders. A shark swimming below saw a roughly oval shape with arms and legs hanging down and paddling. This is very similar to sea lions (the main prey of great white sharks) or sea turtles (a common food for tiger sharks).</p>','Survival-1','','inherit','closed','closed','','215-revision-v1','','','2021-08-26 12:33:19','2021-08-26 12:33:19','',215,'http://BE3BB933-395F-41E6-80BA-029C3AD574E1',0,'revision','',0),(796,4,'2021-08-26 12:35:09','2021-08-26 12:35:09','<h1>SharkPedia</h1>		\n			<h2>Watch out for sharks</h2>		\n		<p>Let us help you learn more about sharks to protect you and your loved ones.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						LEARN MORE\n					</a>\n			<h2><a href=\"/services/#service-1\">survival skills</a></h2>		\n			<h2><a href=\"/services/#service-2\">beach recommendations</a></h2>		\n			<h2><a href=\"/services/#service-3\">shark album</a></h2>		\n                    <h4 style=\"text-align: center; color: #000000;\">Shark attacks by Gender</h4>\n                    <h4 style=\"text-align: left; color: #000000;\">Shark attacks Type</h4>\n			<h2>search Beachs</h2>		\n		<p>Find out about the distribution of sharks on the beach, the history of accidents near the beach and the nearest hospital for your safety.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Search\n					</a>\n			<figure class=\'gallery-item\'>\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"4d9d9662\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\"fiona-ayerst-TdENDAHtPBw-unsplash\" href=\'http://sharkpedia.